name: EUR-Other
objective: The primary goal  is to promote democratic and free market transitions in the former communist countries of Central and Eastern Europe and EUrasia, enabling them to overcome their past and become reliable, productive members of the Euro-Atlantic community of Western democracies.

authorizations.text: 111, 117, 634A, Department of State, Foreign Operations, and Related Programs Appropriations Act of 2010. 75 Stat. 424. Pub. L. 87, 194. 22 U.S.C. § 2151. 111, 117, 634A, Foreign Assistance Act of 1961.
